snippet.title: AEW: Fight Forever | Season Pass 3 Trailer
snippet.description:
Get ready for a complete new season in AEW: Fight Forever. Season Pass 3 includes access to even more AEW wrestlers, the all-new day and evening beach maps, new skins and attire options, loads of new moves and premium music tracks.
- Swerve to the Beach
- Giant Swing in the Ring
- Hayter's Gunna Game
- Freebie for da Fans

The Season Pass 3 Content Breakdown:
 - Swerve Strickland
 - Claudio Castagnoli
 - Jamie Hayter
 - Day and Evening Beach Maps
 - 33 brand new moves
 - 42 new skin and attire options
 - 11 all new music tracks
